extracted_snippet:
{'original': 'I want to take a moment to highlight two incredible employees at the Walmart on 40 Hwy. First, Ms. Deb absolutely deserves her kudos. That woman is truly a customer service queen. During the busy holiday rush, another shopper and I were searching for poultry seasoning. The shelf was empty, but Deb did not stop there—she continued searching high and low until she finally found what we needed. I know she spent at least 10 minutes helping us, and she did it with patience and kindness the entire time. That kind of dedication is rare, and it made a huge difference.

I also want to recognize Jeremy, who was just as impressive. I asked him where to find an item, and instead of pointing, he personally walked me straight to it. Quick, attentive, and helpful—exactly what excellent service looks like.

Let me just say, the Walmart on 40 Hwy feels completely restored. It’s like walking into a brand new store, and the employees are a huge part of that experience. Thank you, Deb and Jeremy, for reminding customers what great service feels like!'}
